#All insturctions for downloading the neccesary resourcses are here!

Python (download from python.org)
Tkinter (If you installed python just do (import tkinter as tk.)Because Tkinter is pre installed)
Tkinter.Scrolled Text (Needs Tkinter To Work. Also preinstalled with tkinter.)
WolframAlpha(download in powershell(pip install wolframalpha))
Wikipedia(download in powershell(pip install wikipedia))

#You will need to import all of these using import to work. Like this

import tkinter as tk
from tkinter.scrolledtext import Scrolledtext
import wikipedia
import wolramalpha

